2026-05-18T06:16:15.8782445Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-18T06:16:15.8783194Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-18T06:16:15.8783945Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-18T06:16:15.8784710Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-18T06:16:15.8785472Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-18T06:16:15.8786227Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-18T06:16:15.8786962Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
