2026-05-18T06:16:16.3004199Z 274            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-05-18T06:16:16.3004541Z 275            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-18T06:16:16.3004866Z 276            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-18T06:16:16.3005197Z 277            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-18T06:16:16.3005411Z 278            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-18T06:16:16.3005778Z 279            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-18T06:16:16.3006319Z 280            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-18T06:16:16.3006643Z 281            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-18T06:16:16.3006958Z 282            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
